item.title: getAllObjects
item.description: SoftLayer_User_Customer_External_Binding_Vendor::getAllObjects Get a list of all available external binding vendors that SoftLayer supports. Overview getAllObjects() will return a list of the available external binding vendors that SoftLayer supports. Use this list to select the appropriate vendor when creating a new external binding.
